  "Extensibility": "<p class=\"opacity-80 mt-4 leading-relaxed\">The SPA navigator in <code>src/modules/attributes/router.ts</code> listens to <code>#hash</code> fragments. Upgrade this to implement the HTML5 History API natively without hash URLs.</p>",
  "Snippet": "<div class=\"p-8 bg-base-200 rounded-box border shadow-inner\">\n    <div class=\"menu menu-horizontal bg-base-100 w-full justify-center rounded-box p-4 gap-4 mb-8 shadow-inner border border-base-300\">\n        <li><a href=\"#/\" class=\"font-bold\" data-class-active=\"activeRoute === '/'\">Dashboard</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#/users\" class=\"font-bold\" data-class-active=\"activeRoute === '/users'\">Users</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#/settings\" class=\"font-bold\" data-class-active=\"activeRoute === '/settings'\">Settings</a></li>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div data-router=\"activeRoute\" class=\"p-12 bg-base-100 rounded-xl border border-primary/20 shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300\">\n        <div data-route=\"/\">\n            <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-primary\">/dashboard</h2>\n            <p class=\"mt-4 opacity-70\">Primary AST context mounted from hash-relative root.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div data-route=\"/users\">\n            <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-secondary\">/users</h2>\n            <p class=\"mt-4 opacity-70\">Dynamic fragment swapped mathematically via hash-change interceptors.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div data-route=\"/settings\">\n            <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-accent\">/settings</h2>\n            <p class=\"mt-4 opacity-70\">Persisted state across virtual routing nodes confirmed.</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>"
